# SportsGPT Project Structure

## Overview
SportsGPT is a Next.js 15 application with TypeScript and Tailwind CSS v4, designed for sports betting assistance.

## Main Files
- [src/app/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx) - Main entry point with view state management
- [src/app/globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css) - Global styles and Tailwind configuration
- [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts) - Next.js configuration with SVG support

## Key Components
- [src/components/landing-page.tsx](mdc:src/components/landing-page.tsx) - Main landing page with team selection
- [src/components/chat-interface.tsx](mdc:src/components/chat-interface.tsx) - Chat conversation interface
- [src/components/team-logos.tsx](mdc:src/components/team-logos.tsx) - Team logo components and mappings
- [src/components/loading-spinner.tsx](mdc:src/components/loading-spinner.tsx) - Page transitions

## UI Components
- [src/components/ui/button.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/button.tsx) - ShadcnUI button component
- [src/components/ui/card.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/card.tsx) - ShadcnUI card component

## Assets
- Team logos are stored in `public/logos/clubes/` directory as SVG files
- Logos follow naming convention: `team-name.svg` (lowercase, hyphenated)

## Design System
- Uses Inter font family
- Black background (#000000) with white text
- Precise spacing following Figma measurements
- Responsive design with mobile-first approach